  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Objective #1: To strengthen the capacity of the women&#x2019;s cooperative in Fadoro Village to serve eight existing self-help groups.  


Objective #2: To improve access of at least 92 women  to savings and credit facilities to run the small-level enterprises in Fadoro village.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to support eight women&#x2019;s self-help groups to gain access to capital to run agricultural enterprises, particularly post-harvest processing of rice and other agricultural products. The project also seeks to strengthen the leadership and accounting skills of the group&#x2019;s management team.</narrative>
